  45:../Backend/gnu-efi-3.0.9/lib/sread.c ****     Opens a file for (simple) reading.  The simple read abstraction
  46:../Backend/gnu-efi-3.0.9/lib/sread.c ****     will access the file either from a memory copy, from a file
  47:../Backend/gnu-efi-3.0.9/lib/sread.c ****     system interface, or from the load file interface. 
  48:../Backend/gnu-efi-3.0.9/lib/sread.c **** 
